## 订阅列表 

这里你可以查看我的订阅列表
```{r, echo = FALSE, message=FALSE, warning = FALSE, results = 'hold'}
library(DT)
m = read.csv("../R/list.txt", colClasses = "character")[, -1]
n = cbind(Blog = m[,2], Author = m[, 3],  m[1])
datatable(n)
```
